  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate postoperative pain in Bascom Cleft Lift operation
      receiving multimodal analgesia in day-case surgery setting.

      Hypothesis: Multimodal analgesia provides adequate pain relief in patients undergoing Bascom
      Cleft Lift operation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
